description:
On today’s show, Emily sits down with the host of Women of Impact & co-founder of Quest Nutrition Lisa Bilyeu to talk about women in business and how her and her partner are the definition of #relationshipgoals.

The two discuss what it’s like to work alongside your partner, but still keep it sexy and healthy, as well as ways that you both can indulge in your “selfish desires.” Plus, they talk about being a strong woman in business who also supports other women – as we all should.
